---
title: Shrimp and Zucchini Linguine with Dill Cream Sauce
description: This all-season dish brings together some of our favourite summer-inspired pairings. The combination of shrimp, zucchini and dill  will have you forgetting all about the chilly temperatures outside.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/linguines-aux-crevettes-et-a-la-courgette-d4e7fce3.jpg
